      "role": "user",
      "content": "Wait, \"assured us that the situation is under control\"? That sounds like we're taking their word for it rather than verifying it. If those militias are just \"posturing,\" why are the field reports looking so messy? If I bet my budget on this 95% confidence level and it turns out those troop movements were actually the precursor to a border skirmish, it's going to be on me. Are you absolutely certain there isn't any raw data you're leaving out just to keep the assessment looking clean?",
